getConnections

public jain.application.services.jcp.JcpConnection[] getConnections()
Return the set of routed or pending (not yet routed) connections. This is synchronized to ensure that Connection.routeConnection() can transfer a pending connection to a routed one without causing "getConnections()" errors.
